# Next.js Standards

- Use Server Components by default. Add `'use client'` only for interactivity.
- Await async `params` in Next.js 16: `params: Promise<{ locale: string }>`.
- Metadata via `generateMetadata` per locale page.
- Server Actions in `src/actions/` with `'use server'`.
- Validate all form input server-side with Zod.
- No secrets in client code — use env vars server-side only.
